data.description: Welcome home to this adorable move in ready 3 bedroom/2 bath home in Navasota. Located at the end of a cul-de-sac on a huge lot, this home has one of the most spacious backyards you will find. New paint and carpet throughout this well maintained beauty makes this home feel brand new. It boasts a wonderfully designed open floor plan, spacious master bedroom with en suite bathroom and gigantic walk in closet. Designated laundry/mud room, and ample closets throughout the house will give you plenty of room for your wardrobe as well as additional storage if needed. Don’t miss out and schedule your private showing today. This Navasota gem is sure to please.
